# Walkthrough: Table Display Improvements

## User Requirements
1. Remove truncation from terms column
2. Focus on commission percentage (%)
3. Show whether brand name can be used (boolean)
4. Make table area wider to display more information

## Changes Made

### Backend Data Schema
Updated [generator.py](file:///C:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos%20mvp/backend/generator.py#L24-L37) prompt templates to generate new fields:

**Previous Schema:**
```json
{
  "brand": "...",
  "incentive": "10% giá trị đơn",
  "terms": "Cấm brand name",
  "legitimacy_score": 85
}
```

**New Schema:**
```json
{
  "brand": "Exness",
  "program_url": "https://...",
  "commission_percent": 40,
  "commission_type": "Revenue Share / CPA",
  "can_use_brand": false,
  "traffic_3m": "25.4M",
  "legitimacy_score": 9.8
}
```

### Frontend Table Component
Updated [ResultsTable.jsx](file:///C:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos%20mvp/frontend/src/components/ResultsTable.jsx) with new column structure:

**New Columns:**
| Column | Display | Description |
|--------|---------|-------------|
| **Hoa hồng (%)** | `40%` in large font | Commission percentage, sortable |
| **Loại HH** | `PERCENTAGE` / `CPA` / `HYBRID` | Commission type in small caps |
| **Brand Name** | ✓ Được / ✗ Không | Green/red badges for brand usage permission |

**Layout Changes:**
- ✅ Removed `max-w-7xl` constraint → Table now uses full width
- ✅ Removed `max-w-[200px] truncate` from terms → No more truncation
- ✅ Commission percentage displayed in `text-2xl font-semibold` → Prominent focus
- ✅ Brand usage shown with colored badges → Easy visual scanning

### Visual Improvements

**Commission Display:**
```jsx
<td className="px-6 py-6 font-mono text-2xl text-white font-semibold">
    {row.commission_percent > 0 ? `${row.commission_percent}%` : '—'}
</td>
```
- Large, bold font for easy readability
- Shows "—" for CPA-only programs (commission_percent = 0)

**Brand Usage Badges:**
```jsx
{row.can_use_brand ? (
    <span className="bg-green-500/20 text-green-400">✓ Được</span>
) : (
    <span className="bg-red-500/20 text-red-400">✗ Không</span>
)}
```
- Green badge: Brand name allowed
- Red badge: Brand name restricted

**Legitimacy Score:**
- Changed from 0-100 scale to 0-10 scale for better readability
- Updated visual bar calculation: [(score / 10) * 100%](file:///C:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/adecos%20mvp/frontend/src/components/ChatMessage.jsx#71-72)

